metadata.name: Devil in Disguise
metadata.description:
Elvis Presley 
Devil in Disguise
Inspired by the cover photo of "(You're the) Devil in Disguise" a  single song by Elvis,,the eternal king of rock and roll, 1963.The drawing technique is pen on paper.

You look like an angel
Walk like an angel
Talk like an angel

But I got wise
You're the devil in disguise
Oh yes you are
The devil in disguise

You're the devil in disguise
Oh yes you are
The devil in disguise
Oh yes you are



Writer(s): Bill Giant, Florence Kaye, Bernie Baum
